DE_FUELWORKS 

by V0lK1

NorthernPetrol(TM) has developed the new generation of fuel:
Every barrel of it is produced with less crude oil than every
other fuel. But the competitors already realized their problem
and commissioned a terrorist group to destroy the main refinery
of NP.

Terrorists:
Plant the C4 either on the crude oil tanks (spot A) or the train
terminal (spot B), which is filled with containers of the fuel.

Counter-Terrorists:
Prevent the Terrorists from planting bombs on the premises
of the factory. If they done so, defuse the explosive charges!
